  "subject": "1.14.0 release",
  "commit_message": "1.14.0 release\n\n- introduce multicloud client bean\n- split up CnfAdapterRest into multiple controllers\n- upgrade to so common 1.17.0-SNAPSHOT\n- improve cnf-adapter test coverage\n- make cnf-adapter instance creation more resilient to failure\n- add integration tests\n- add otel agent\n- update so common dependencies\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4293\nChange-Id: I8ab1317f76ae67c292826270c2a1a35dc87a29cd\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
